{
  "stem": "23572.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We always used to-- I forgot her name.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Maybe I knew her name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I have no idea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I don't think she was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But later on, after 1933 or whenever the racial laws came out in Nuremberg with the Nazis, you couldn't even have-- you could not employ a non-Jewish housekeeper.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we didn't have a-- [NON-ENGLISH] we didn't have anybody.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I remember my mother laying out, making challah.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "OK, and I remember her-- for spaghetti, she used to take the dough and just spread it over the table.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I very well-- going to get a chicken, had to show her-- everything was strictly kosher.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And fish.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She made her own gefilte fish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Not like today.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was no Manischewitz to open up, the boxes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She did all this cooking.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She was a very good cook.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh my.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember my favorite dish anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think I liked gefilte fish, and I like sweets to this day.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I have no recollection of a favorite dish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not that they affected us directly-- affected me directly as a kid.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was-- but I remember in school, I have some memories.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because the first four years Hitler came to power, I was in public school.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And two things I remember.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I could not go with the children for swimming lessons.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because as a Jew, I was polluting the pool.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I have to admit, I'm ashamed to say, to this day, I don't know how to swim.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And all my kids born here were lifeguards at one time or another.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Somehow I developed a fear of the water.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's the one thing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The other thing I remember, in school, I was always very good in the German language and geography.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
